Flowers are blooming
Smell the whole mind
you are mine
How much is yours?
Friends if not seen
don't talk
Twelve flowers in twelve months
Fuitta remains on the branch
Aise Nagar in this way
Reading in the evening
Bhoma lives in any country
sitting in a garden
To eat the honey of any or flowers
Worms keep coming
Go see the city of gold
Equal to the moon 

💔Kakoli💔
